S.FORM: matatengil kakitizaan nu Sakizaya demiad 2018.03.11 14:30 17:30 kakitizaan Nabakuwan (Kalingku) a se Sakul niyazu' Kofuli Saungay nu binawlan teban a luma' u heci nu matatengil 1.Walewalelan: itiza iteban nu Tungao atu Hanpen . walel sananay ku uway nu bila'. wale walel an, yadah ku walel i buyu', sisa pangangan tu Walewalelan. naayaway a babalaki tayni miadup atu milami', maazih itini yadah ku walel, sisa, panganganen ku Walewalelan. tina kakitizaan itiza i Yilan a kuwan, ayza sa u Talukuay a subal tuway. amis 24"30'12.91, wali 121"50'04.35 katukuh amis 24"29'49.32 wali 121"49'43.00, ilaed 640m. 2.Lalabian ipabaw nu Sakul niyazu', i buyubuyuan, i masazukuay nu buyu'. sakamusa ku babalaki, natayza miadup atu milami' i buyu', anu caykaletep taluma', itiza tu milabin. sisa, panganganen ku Lalabian. 3.Kamukamulan ipabaw nu buyu' nu Katangka. kamul sananay u kilang , si sangelacay a balu, bangcalay a kilang, u Ngayngayay cidekay a kilang. amis 24"02'20.14 wali 121"34'15.85
